  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 14-15 Guests</strong></p>
<p>The Chalet Pregentil is a delightful and charming property, situated in the heart of the old village of Alpe d'Huez.</p>
<p>The chalet interior enjoys a wonderful cosy atmosphere, and being made virtually entirely from local wood, provides a genuine sense of rustic Alpine charm. At the end of a hard day on the slopes, guests can relax in the sauna.</p>
<p>Bedrooms are prettily furnished in traditional wooden style, and most enjoy en suite facilities. Rooms 5 and 6 share a hallway, bathroom with a shower and wc as well as a small private lounge area so can be combined to make a suite, ideal for a family or a small group of friends. (Access is narrow to Rooms 1, 2 and 3 on the lower ground floor).</p>
<p>After dinner, the après-ski can be reached easily by a few minutes' stroll to the busy nightlife and the many bars of Alpe d'Huez. For ski access the nearby 'Telecentre' ski-lift will take you directly to the foot of the main lifts and ski school meeting point. At the end of the day you can ski back to within 150 metres of the chalet door.</p>]]></description>
