  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation Summary</strong>:</p>
<p><strong>Lower Ground Floor</strong><br /><strong>Room 1 </strong>- Twin with en suite shower/wc</p>
<p><strong>Room 2</strong> - Twin with en suite shower/wc</p>
<p><strong>Room 3</strong> - Twin with en suite shower/wc</p>
<p><img src="/media/13061155/france_alpe-dhuez_chalet_pregentil_lower_ground-floor.jpg" alt="Chalet Pregentil Lower Ground Floor Floorplan" align="absmiddle" /></p>
<p><strong>Ground Floor</strong> <br />Entrance with ski and boot racks, sauna, open-plan lounge and dining area with a balcony</p>
<p><strong>Room 4</strong> - Twin with en suite shower/wc</p>
<p><img src="/media/13061154/france_alpe-dhuez_chalet_pregentil_ground-floor.jpg" alt="Chalet Pregentil Ground Floor Floorplan" align="absmiddle" /></p>
<p><strong>First Floor</strong></p>
<p><strong>Room 5 </strong>- Double (sharing shower/wc with room 6)</p>
<p><strong>Room 6</strong> - Twin (sharing shower/wc with room 5)</p>
<p><strong>Rooms 5 &amp; 6</strong> can be combined to form a suite with small lounge and balcony</p>
<p><strong>Room 7</strong> - Triple (sleeps 2-3) under the eaves with en suite shower/wc.**</p>
<p>**Triple rooms are recommended for a maximum of 2 adults and 1 child</p>
<p><img src="/media/13061153/france_alpe-dhuez_chalet_pregentil_first-floor.jpg" alt="Chalet Pregentil First Floor Floorplan" align="absmiddle" /></p>
<p>Please note that this chalet is licensed for 15 people only including infants</p>
<p>N.B.: Floor plans are for guidance only and are not to scale.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
